        "text": "HubSpot AI offers a highly generous free tier including a CRM, AI content assistant, chatbot builder, and marketing automation. Rank Math's free WordPress SEO plugin rivals paid alternatives. GetResponse offers a free plan with basic email marketing features."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Can AI marketing tools replace human marketers?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "AI marketing tools dramatically improve efficiency but work best as force multipliers for human marketers. They excel at data analysis, content generation, optimization, and automation — while strategic decisions, creative direction, and relationship building still require human expertise."
      }
    },
    {
