        "text": "Rank Math is free for its core WordPress SEO plugin (paid Pro starts at $59/year). HubSpot's free tier includes CRM and AI content generation. GetResponse starts at just $19/month for email marketing. For a full-featured AI marketing suite, Writesonic starts at $20/month."
