<h3>Test Results</h3>
<p><strong>Prompt used:</strong> "Find 50 long-tail keyword opportunities for a B2B SaaS company targeting the term 'AI content generator'"</p>
<ul>
<li>Keyword ideas generated: 950+ in under 3 seconds</li>
<li>Keyword Difficulty accuracy: 9/10 — closely matched real SERP difficulty</li>
<li>Content draft quality: 8.5/10 — well-structured SEO-optimized output</li>
<li>Competitive gap analysis: 9.5/10 — surfaced 23 high-value opportunities</li>
<li>Site audit comprehensiveness: 9/10 — 140+ checkpoints</li>
</ul>

